    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Processing Pipeline\nFor each deal: Get Deal + Associations > Extract IDs > Batch Read Line Items > Format (Name - Qty X - Price - Closed Won on DATE) > Get Company > Append > Update Company",
        "height": 140,
